From b7a21d30d5645ab289d609c2e52a67b42d203dce Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: David Edmundson <kde@davidedmundson.co.uk>
Date: Mon, 20 Apr 2026 11:03:30 +0100
Subject: [PATCH] Eis: Support 1.6 additions

1.6 adds support for arbitrary keysyms and text.

keysyms uses a tested path used by fakeinput already, text is sent via
text input if available, falling back to fake keysyms.

This also adds a new unit test for libei.
